  "text": "I think it might be a good idea if we uh terminated the contact at this time and to allow the instrument to gain more necessary energy before continuing. This is my decision at this time. I would very much like to continue contact, but it seems to me, although I can't tell the instrument's level, that the instrument should not uh use up any more energy. I am raponding to an unasked query however it is most salient and therefore we beg your forgiveness for this infringement. The energy has been lost to the instrument dedicated to this purpose only. You may do as you will, but this is the nature of the instrument's preparation for contact and is the sole reason we may use it.",
